All snack board enthusiasts know: a balance of sweet and savory is key! We whipped up a seasonal snack board with @cafigs and Feedfeed’s @clarelangan. 
👉 Did you know California Fresh Fig season is now thru November? When you see them, buy them! Find @cafigs near you by visiting your local grocery retailer. 
👉 Want more fig inspo? Check out our Fig Feed! https://thefeedfeed.com/figs and follow @cafigs #feedfeed #figs

node.text:
Use @filippoberio_us for all of your baking needs (#ad)! Heart-healthy #FilippoBerio Olive Oil takes butter’s place, which is what’s traditionally used in pie dough, for these Balsamic, Blackberry, and Ricotta Hand Pies. The olive oil sub along with the use of #vegan ricotta cheese makes this a #dairyfree treat! The recipe makes 8 of the cutest personal pies, perfect for summer picnics and days outdoors.

👉Get the recipe by clicking the link in our bio or by visiting ff.recipes/fb-handpies #feedfeed #oliveoil #hearthealthy #pie #feedfeed #blackberry #baking #smallbatch

You haven't tasted cinnamon until you've tried Single Origin by @SimplyOrganicFoods Vietnamese Cinnamon (#ad). It has a strong, sweet, and rich flavor that works well in everything from cocktails to savory applications. This Cinnamon Scented Iced Coffee is inspired by traditional Vietnamese coffee and it is sure to become a favorite for a morning or afternoon pick-me-up!
👆Get the recipe by clicking the link in our bio or by visiting ff.recipes/cinn-vietnamese-coffee
👉To learn more about @SimplyOrganicFoods and their new Single Origin Line, visit ff.recipes/so-singleorigin
Recipe by Team Feedfeed's Senior Food Editor @mollyjeanadams 
🎥 & 📷 by Team Feedfeed's @hungryforhistory and @lmsthompson 
#feedfeed #simplyorganic #simplyorganicfoods #cinnamon #caffiene #coffee #icedcoffee #coffeelover

node.text:
This epic Ice Cream Cake by @mollyjeanadams was inspired by Spumoni; a classic Italian dessert made with layers of gelato or ice cream. Usually spumoni features layers of chocolate, cherry and pistachio gelato and may include a few additional delicious mix-ins like sponge cake, chopped nuts or fruit like Maraschino cherries. This version features a Cookies & Cream Crust, Chocolate Ice Cream, Chocolate Cookie Crumbs, Pistachio Ice Cream, Chopped Pistachios and finally a layer of Strawberry Ice Cream.  How could you go wrong?!
🛍Tap the photo to shop our faves and visit shop.thefeedfeed.com for gifts, goodies and more!
👉 Link in bio for recipe
🌟 Keep tagging #feedfeed @thefeedfeed for a chance to be featured

node.text:
🎉 CONTEST TIME w/ @Think_Rice! (#ad) Check out the epic prizes below👇 September is #NationalRiceMonth and we want to see how you're enjoying rice all month long! We’re talking fried rice, paella, burrito bowls, soup, sushi and more. @jennygoycochea's got the right idea with this insane Lobster Risotto - now it's your turn! What are you cooking up with your rice?
👉TO ENTER:
1) Follow @thefeedfeed & @Think_Rice 
2) Show us your best rice dishes by uploading an image to Instagram and tagging @thefeedfeed @Think_Rice #ThinkRice #feedfeed & #contest (hashtags must be in the main caption of a new Instagram post).
🎉THREE Grand Prize Winners will each receive the below prizes valued at over $1,000:
* @Think_Rice Swag
* @shuncutlery 5-Piece Knife Set and Block
* @lenox French Carved 16-Piece Dining Set
* @aromahousewares 8-Cup Rice Cooker
* Variety Pack of U.S.-grown Rice
Contest will close September 30, 2021 at 11:59PM ET.
👉Full contest details: ff.recipes/think-rice-contest
👉Get the recipe: ff.recipes/lobster-risotto
#feedfeed #rice #usgrown #risotto #lobster #glutenfree #glutenfreerecipe #thinkrice
